org.linqs.psl.model.term

Interface Attribute

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comparable<Constant>, Constant, SummationVariableOrTerm, Term
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DateAttribute, DoubleAttribute, IntegerAttribute, LongAttribute, StringAttribute

    public interface Attribute
extends Constant
    A Constant that is a value, as opposed to a UniqueID.

    For example, people in a social network should probably be represented as UniqueIDs, but their properties, such as names or ages, should probably be Attributes.

    Author:
    Matthias Broecheler
